---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---

<PageLayout title="Transitions" slug="transitions">
  <div class="monologue">
    This page is to explore ideas for transitions.
  </div>

  <section class="demo-section">
    <div class="demo-header">
      <h2>Dimensional expansion</h2>
      <a href={`${base}/demos/transitions/index.html`} target="_blank" rel="noopener">open full size ↗</a>
    </div>
    <div class="demo-embed">
      <iframe src={`${base}/demos/transitions/index.html?embedded`} title="Dimensional expansion" scrolling="no"></iframe>
    </div>
    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        The core idea: expanding outward from a concentrated form reads as a transition from 2D to 3D.
        A flat strip gains depth as it widens — as if a surface is unfolding into the third dimension.
      </p>
      <p>
        The surface itself is built by spatial Fourier synthesis. Multiple sine waves propagate outward
        from different source points, and their interference defines the height field. Each wave adds a
        harmonic — the shape gets richer as more components arrive.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
